													<li>Statistical identification of differentially expressed genes (DEGs) with edgeR or DESeq2</li>
													<li>PCA plots, Venn diagram</li>
													<li>Gene clustering and heatmaps</li>
												</ul>
												<li>Step 6 - Functional Interpretation:</li>
												<ul class="level-2">
